snippet.title: 'individualism in the dead-internet age' Game Trailer
snippet.description:
https://alienmelon.itch.io/shovelware
"Individualism in the dead-internet age" is a short-form Backrooms-style horror interactive-essay-meets-walking-sim about technocapitalism and the things we lost along the way.
Follow coins under the electric mist of a clouded starry sky. Discover hyper-links. Listen to the words both inside and outside your head. Seal your fate before the productivity machine. Together we can defeat the machine!
